oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Wrestling; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Order letter from the Wrestling office requesting 100 1-color window cards for the World's Greatest NWA Wrestling at the Western Kentucky Fairgrounds Convention Center in Hopkinsville, KY on Thursday, June 22, 1978. Events include six man tag battle: Dutch Mintell, Ken Lucas, Bobby Eaton vs. Gypsy Joe, Ron Garfield, Merican Angel with Mgr. Las Vegas Louie. Semi Final Match: Jerry Barber vs. Whipper Watson; Arvill Hutto vs. Eric Embry. Nick Gulas Promotor.
